      "id": "K001",
      "title": "Vue 3 组合式 API 核心概念",
      "category": "programming",
      "tags": [
        "Vue",
        "前端",
        "JavaScript"
      ],
      "content": "## Vue 3 组合式 API\n\n### ref vs reactive\n- `ref()` 用于基本类型，需 `.value` 访问\n- `reactive()` 用于对象，直接访问属性\n- `computed()` 派生计算状态\n\n### 生命周期\n- `onMounted()`, `onUnmounted()`, `onUpdated()`\n\n### watch vs watchEffect\n- `watch()` 显式指定监听源\n- `watchEffect()` 自动追踪依赖",
      "source": {
        "type": "article",
        "title": "Vue 3 官方文档",
        "url": "https://cn.vuejs.org/guide/extras/composition-api-faq.html"
      },
      "relatedEntries": [
