    {
      "id": "K002",
      "title": "Python f-string 高级技巧",
      "category": "programming",
      "tags": [
        "Python",
        "字符串"
      ],
      "content": "## f-string 技巧\n\n### 格式化数字\n```python\nnum = 3.14159\nprint(f\"pi={num:.2f}\")  # pi=3.14\nprint(f\"{1000000:,}\")   # 1,000,000\n```\n\n### 对齐与填充\n```python\nname = \"阿财\"\nprint(f\"{name:>10}\")   # 右对齐\nprint(f\"{name:*^10}\")  # 居中填充*\n```\n\n### 调试输出\n```python\nprint(f\"{x=}, {y=}\")  # x=10, y=20\n```",
      "source": {
        "type": "article",
        "title": "Real Python: f-strings Guide",
        "url": "https://realpython.com/python-f-strings/"
      },
      "relatedEntries": [],
      "status": "published",
      "createdAt": "2026-05-01",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-01"
