    {
      "id": "K004",
      "title": "GIS 中常见的坐标系及其转换",
      "category": "gis",
      "tags": [
        "GIS",
        "坐标系",
        "测绘"
      ],
      "content": "## 常见坐标系\n\n### WGS84 (EPSG:4326)\n- GPS 使用的经纬度坐标系\n- 地心坐标系\n\n### Web Mercator (EPSG:3857)\n- 网络地图常用投影\n- Google Maps, 高德, 百度均使用\n- 特点：越靠近两极变形越大\n\n### CGCS2000 (EPSG:4490)\n- 中国大地坐标系 2000\n- 国家测绘基准\n\n### 坐标转换\n```python\nfrom pyproj import Transformer\ntransformer = Transformer.from_crs(4326, 3857)\nx, y = transformer.transform(lat, lon)\n```",
      "source": {
        "type": "book",
        "title": "测绘学基础",
        "url": ""
      },
